customer_service_info.checkout_explanation:
When you buy these tickets, your payment will go directly to Razorgator. RazorGator will send you a confirmation message and deliver the tickets to you.

If you have any questions about your order, you can contact RazorGator customer support by phone or email.
When you buy these tickets, your payment will go directly to Crowdseats.

When you buy these tickets, your payment will go directly to UberSeat. UberSeat will send you a confirmation message and deliver the tickets to you.

If you have any questions about your order, you can contact UberSeat customer support by phone or email.
When you buy these tickets, your payment will go directly to Fanxchange.

When you buy these tickets, your payment will go directly to Telecharge. SeatGeek will send you a confirmation message and Telecharge will deliver the tickets to you. A charge will appear on your credit card as 'Telecharge - SeatGeek (New York)'.

If you have any questions about your order, you can contact Telecharge customer support by phone or email.
When you buy these tickets, your payment will go directly to Primesport.
When you buy these tickets, your payment will go directly to Wantickets.
